metadata.name: [ Bianca ] New Year - 1st Anniversary Celebration
metadata.description:
「 Bianca & Tiger 」
.* 1st Anniversary Celebration Art *. 

Once upon a time in Ozania, there was a yearly ritual on the New Year Festival. The ritual was a random selection of sacred animals that would predict the life and fortune of that year. 

Auspicious beast of 2022 :《Pᚨᚾᛏᚺᛖᚱᚨ ᛏᛁᚷᚱᛁᛊ》 

• Type : Snow Tiger of The West
• Sex : Female
• Name : Frostine
• Summoner : Bianca — The Assassin Maid

*.•.༓ ༒ ------- ༒ ༓.•.*

This year the 𝖙𝖎𝖌𝖊𝖗 is the symbol of our fate, representing strength, great power, and good luck. However, this fortune will come with great sacrifice; as blood would spill, people harmed, and lives taken.

                                 " Cheers to 2022 "
